data.description: Large lot located right at the edge of  town in Nashwauk. Modern updates are present with new flooring, paint, kitchen cabinets and appliances throughout. 3 bedrooms, with a large master bedroom and bathroom. Open living concept with eat in kitchen and dining area, large living room with windows looking over deck with slider door. Simple living all on one level with 2 stall garage and wrap around drive way. Call today for your personal tour.
